Robert Frazer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Frazer 0 Robert W. Frazer (born Robert William Browne on June 29, 1891 in Worcester, Massachusetts – August 17, 1944 in Los Angeles, California) was an American actor who appeared in some 224 shorts and films from the 1910s. He began in films with the Eclair company which released through Universal Pictures.
